          <actionDate>2018-03-07</actionDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Restoring Local Control Act </strong></p> <p>This bill modifies representational and structural requirements for metropolitan planning organizations (MPOs) under the federal-aid highways and public transportation programs. MPOs are policy-making organizations designated to carry out the transportation planning process for each urban area with a population of at least 50,000. </p>]]></text>
        </item>
